6  BC ). (iv) it has also been traced back to other ethnic groups in northern China."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Gratnatch Mac Martachus was born about 1020, in Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland as the son of Martachus Mormaer of Mar. He had at least 1 son."},"et":{"about 1020–":"umbes 1020–Surnud","1020–Male":"1020–Surnud","1040–Male":"1040–Surnud","0995–Male":"0995–Surnud","0995":"0995","1020":"1020","1040":"1040","about 1020":"umbes 1020","Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland"},"fi":{"about 1020–":"noin 1020–Kuollut","1020–Male":"1020–Kuollut","1040–Male":"1040–Kuollut","0995–Male":"0995–Kuollut","0995":"0995","1020":"1020","1040":"1040","about 1020":"noin 1020","Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland"},"fr":{"about 1020–":"environ 1020–Décédé","1020–Male":"1020–Décédé","1040–Male":"1040–Décédé","0995–Male":"0995–Décédé","0995":"0995","1020":"1020","1040":"1040","about 1020":"environ 1020","Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Écosse","lifeSummary":"Gratnatch Mac Martachus est né environ 1020, à Dunfermline, Fife, Écosse, fils de Martachus Mormaer of Mar. Il a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"about 1020–":"um 1020–Verstorben","1020–Male":"1020–Verstorben","1040–Male":"1040–Verstorben","0995–Male":"0995–Verstorben","0995":"0995","1020":"1020","1040":"1040","about 1020":"um 1020","Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland","lifeSummary":"Gratnatch Mac Martachus wurde um 1020 in Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland, als Sohn von Martachus Mormaer of Mar geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"about 1020–":"about 1020–Desede","1020–Male":"1020–Desede","1040–Male":"1040–Desede","0995–Male":"0995–Desede","0995":"0995","1020":"1020","1040":"1040","about 1020":"about 1020","Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland"},"hu":{"about 1020–":"1020 körül–elhunyt","1020–Male":"1020–elhunyt","1040–Male":"1040–elhunyt","0995–Male":"0995–elhunyt","0995":"0995","1020":"1020","1040":"1040","about 1020":"1020 körül","Dun